<h1> Reading and Schedule for Making the Bomb</h1><p>
<p>
<br>

This will change.  Check back often.<p>

Please also see the <a href="assignments.html">list of assignments and
due dates</a>.<p>


For the reading for Rhodes, two questions we'll consider frequently are:
<ol>
<li>Why do you think Rhodes includes what he does in each chapter?
<li>What did you think was the most interesting and/or important thing
from the reading, and why?
</ol>

